38:51.538 --> 38:53.456
Hey, um...

38:53.456 --> 38:55.083
[ Chuckles ] Yeah?

38:55.083 --> 38:57.168
♪ Even when you tell lies,
tell lies ♪

38:57.168 --> 38:59.587
You and Nolan ‐‐

38:59.587 --> 39:01.130
