to give praise.

39:07.345 --> 39:09.264
Oh.

39:09.264 --> 39:11.599
Well, thank you.

39:11.599 --> 39:13.393
What else do you appreciate
about me?

39:13.393 --> 39:15.436
That you know
when not to push your luck.

39:15.436 --> 39:17.397
Yes. Okay. Good night.

39:17.397 --> 39:18.481
Good night.
Good night.

