39:40.420 --> 39:41.588
[ Jack crying ]

39:41.588 --> 39:45.008
♪ For years to come ♪
[ Sighs ]

39:45.008 --> 39:46.843
♪ You‐ou‐ou ♪

39:46.843 --> 39:47.719
♪ You‐ou‐ou‐ou‐ou ♪

39:47.719 --> 39:49.470
You still love me, right?

39:49.470 --> 39:51.472
♪♪

39:51.472 --> 39:54.183
♪ No matter the distance,
wherever you are ♪

39:54.183 --> 39:56.144
[ Furniture scraping ]

39:56.144 --> 39:58.438
Tamara? Do you need help?

39:58.438 --> 40:00.690
Tamara: Nope.
[ Chuckling ] Okay.

40:00.690 --> 40:02.775
[ Scraping continues ]

40:02.775 --> 40:05.236
♪♪

40:05.236 --> 40:07.739
♪ And I'll be here for you ♪

40:07.739 --> 40:09.741
Are you sure?

40:09.741 --> 40:11.868
Okay, I'm done.

40:11.868 --> 40:13.328
Promise me
you won't be mad.

40:13.328 --> 40:15.580
Of course. I‐I promise.

40:15.580 --> 40:17.540
Okay. Uh...

40:17.540 --> 40:21.586
♪ I'll be here for you,
