40:21.586 --> 40:23.838
♪ You‐ou‐ou ♪

40:23.838 --> 40:26.966
♪ You‐ou‐ou‐ou‐ou ♪

40:26.966 --> 40:29.052
♪ I'll be here for you... ♪

40:29.052 --> 40:30.595
Do you like it?

40:30.595 --> 40:31.846
Uh...

40:31.846 --> 40:32.972
[ Exhales sharply ]

40:32.972 --> 40:35.058
No. I...

40:35.058 --> 40:36.267
I love it.

40:36.267 --> 40:39.020
♪ Even in death,
I hope you always know ♪

40:39.020 --> 40:41.564
♪ That I was here for you ♪

40:41.564 --> 40:44.150
♪♪

40:44.150 --> 40:48.404
♪ And I'll be here for you,
for years to come ♪

40:48.404 --> 40:51.658
I know breaking up over text
isn't super mature.

40:51.658 --> 40:53.326
No. It's ‐‐ It's fine.

40:53.326 --> 40:55.495
