40:58.915 --> 41:01.000
You're ‐‐ You're great.

41:01.000 --> 41:03.878
You're funny and handsome.

41:03.878 --> 41:05.630
Warm. Smart.

41:05.630 --> 41:07.757
Confused.

41:07.757 --> 41:10.343
It's just ‐‐
I'm good at a lotta things.

41:10.343 --> 41:13.096
