the same way.

41:15.390 --> 41:17.308
We'll start dating.
You'll open up.

41:17.308 --> 41:18.768
I'll distract you
with jokes

41:18.768 --> 41:20.812
so you don't notice
that I'm keeping you away,

41:20.812 --> 41:22.313
