41:28.778 --> 41:30.363
And you'll leave it.

41:30.363 --> 41:33.324
So, you know,
I thought I'd skip to the end.

41:33.324 --> 41:35.493
Wow.

41:35.493 --> 41:36.703
That sounds like a lot.

41:36.703 --> 41:38.705
Well, that's me.
I'm a lot.

41:38.705 --> 41:40.373
Yeah, thing is,
I‐I'm not believing it.

41:40.373 --> 41:42.250
I mean, that you're bad
at relationships ‐‐

41:42.250 --> 41:44.127
