moving forward.

41:58.266 --> 42:00.935
So, really,
the question here is:

42:00.935 --> 42:03.771
Do I make you want to show up
differently?

42:03.771 --> 42:08.943
And...so that you know,
if you say that I do...

42:08.943 --> 42:10.445
I'm all in.

42:10.445 --> 42:12.405
Well...

42:12.405 --> 42:14.532
when you put it that way.

42:14.532 --> 42:17.785
♪ I'll be here for you,
for years to come ♪

